title: The One Where Lala Goes On Tour & Watches The Kardashians For The 1st Time
description:
The Give Them Lala tour launched with a bang and a total vibe in Irvine last week, and Lala shares some of the highlights and a couple of great behind-the-scenes moments! Ocean made a very cute cameo, Kristen Doute, Katie Maloney, and Brittany Cartwright were hilarious, and the Q+A slayed! Lala also experienced another first in her life – she finally watched The Kardashians and shares her thoughts. And she asked for dating app feedback and got plenty! She shares your stories and whether or not she’s changed her mind about giving dating apps a try.
